Multi-step signup. 3 steps total. Clean, minimal design. No step indicators needed — just flows naturally.

### STEP 1 — Your Account
Fields:
- First name (required)
- Last name (required)  
- Work email (required, validate format)
- Password (required, min 8 chars, show strength indicator: weak/fair/strong)
- Confirm password (required, must match, eye icon toggle for both fields)

Validation:
- Password strength: weak = <8 chars or common word, fair = 8+ mixed, strong = 12+ with symbol+number
- Show red error if passwords don't match on blur
- Enforce work email — block gmail/yahoo/hotmail/outlook with message "Please use your work email"

### STEP 2 — Your Company
